Unown (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0200: Misdreavus
Pokémon
#0202: Wobbuffet →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Unown (TCG Pocket).

Unown has been featured on 92 different cards since it debuted in the Neo Discovery expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Unown cards are normally Psychic-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Unown

Unown
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
